        {
            "id": 6031554,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉台積電甩尾翻紅漲42點守住2萬2 周線仍收黑跌27點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股 19 日休市，受以伊衝突升溫，美國川普決議在 2 周內決議是否介入引外界關注，也讓台股今 (20) 日受連假前賣壓沉重影響，以平盤 22,013 點開出後，早盤開低震盪，盤中跌幅加劇，一度跌逾 230 點，所幸尾盤在台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 甩尾急拉下，台股終場小漲 42.24 點或 0.19%，收 22,045.74 點，守住半年線，成交量放大至 4,458 億元；但周線仍收黑，全周下跌 27.21 點。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6031554/l/f0f7c1f220c895fe6b619ff6430d9cfd.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉台積電甩尾翻紅漲42點守住2萬2 周線仍收黑跌27點。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>盤面上，權值股台積電今日又扮演「護國神山」任務，開盤後股價翻黑震盪，盤中一度跌逾 1％，尾盤有大單敲進急拉收紅 K，漲逾 20 元或 1.93%，收 1,055 元，一舉收復 5 日線。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><span style=\"color:#000000\">其他電子權值股方面漲跌互見，緯創 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3231-TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">) 受惠竹北 AI 園區挹注利多漲逾 2.59%，聯詠 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3034:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3034\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3034-TW</a>)、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%；聯發科 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2454 -TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">)、台達電 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2308 -TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">) 跌逾 1%；亞翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6189-TW</a>) 則手握逾千億元訂單，對營運前景樂觀，帶動股價飆至漲停達 294 元，預先展開法說行情。</span></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><span style=\"color:#000000\">航運股部分，受中東情勢尚未明朗，伊朗考慮封鎖海峽，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/eod/detail/BDI\">BDI 指數</a>走弱加深散裝、貨櫃航運的走跌，貨櫃三雄的長榮 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2603-TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">) 跌 2.34%、陽明 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2609-TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">) 跌 1.48%，台船 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2208\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2208-TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">)、慧洋 - KY(</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2637\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2637-TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">)、亞航 (</span><a href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2637\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2630 -TW</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">) 跌逾 3%。</span><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">油電燃氣類股、塑化股也受地緣不穩影響，南亞、台化跌逾 2-3%，</span></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">除了權值股，台股今日中小型類股部分，以台積電設備股及生技股表現最佳，均華 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6640:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6640\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6640-TW</a>) 大漲 7.3％，漢唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2404:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2404\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2404-TW</a>)、萬潤 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6187:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6187\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6187-TW</a>) 漲逾 2-3%。</span></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><span style=\"color:#000000\">生技股則包括股王保瑞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6472:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6472\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6472-TW</a>) 今日除息順利完成填息，收盤更大漲逾 3％，生技族群的台新藥 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6838:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6838\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6838-TW</a>)、霈方 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6574:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6574\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6574-TW</a>)、台康生技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6589:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6589\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6589-TW</a>) 等更以漲停強勢作收。</span></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>分析師表示，今日台股受中東情勢、放假前賣壓沉重，盤中震盪較大，觀察短期均線仍維持偏多架構，投資人可關注盤面上個股熱門題材，持續以短多熱門標的，搭配技術面操作因應。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
